92e-20, \"text\": \"Bia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thai_baht\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thai_baht\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we highlighted last week, they are promising to be one of the most dynamic duos in NWSL - up there withLynn Williamsand Jessica McDonald, or Sam Kerr andYuki Nagasato, if not better.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2946, \"end\": 2950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0352037136128481e-31, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BIA WITH HER FIRST BRACE \\u270c\\ufe0f@biazanerattoputting on an absolute show.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@NWSL|#KCBABYpic.twitter.com/mRwtMoIpru  - KC Current (@thekccurrent)April 21, 2024    Racing Louisvillealso remains undefeated, getting their first win under Bev Yanez in dominating fashion with a 5-1 victory over theUtah Royalsat home.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3116, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0352037136128481e-31, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}, {\"begin\": 3274, \"end\": 3283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beverly_Goebel_Yanez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bev Yanez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beverly_Goebel_Yanez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beverly_Goebel_Yanez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Best of all, they had a record crowd of11,365 in attendance.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like when you watch a win like that, you are going to want to come back.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, aftera shake-up in the technical staff for Portland, with Mike Norris now serving as the club's technical director and Rob Gale appointed interim head coach, the Thorns bounced back with intent against the Dash.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3547, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Timbers\", \"score\": 0.9999993226313129, \"rank\": 6.773692727172181e-07, \"text\": \"Portland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Timbers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Timbers\"}, {\"begin\": 3562, \"end\": 3573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Norris_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.736796676263465, \"rank\": 0.3572228443448427, \"text\": \"Mike Norris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Norris_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Norris_(baseball)\"}, {\"begin\": 3623, \"end\": 3631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Gale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rob Gale\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Gale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rob_Gale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WithChristine Sinclairscoring the first goal on Saturday night, then Smith,Olivia MoultrieandJanine Beckieall finding the back of the net, it was a reminder of the true potential of the team.\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a difference a week makes.\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentenc